{"tid":1259352,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[多​​7分鐘]《復仇者聯盟4（Avengers 4）》重映版海報曝光 上面寫著“我們愛你3000遍”","createTime":"2019-06-26T14:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T01:16:55.000Z","uid":75050,"like":38,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"ede7da4af9d458606684c78aaa8d92e1d1a7134b","tid":1259352,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:21:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2367178156886025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2367178156886025&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkroGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=96787574\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2367178156886025</a><br />\n<br />\n《復仇者聯盟4（Avengers 4）》重映版海報曝光，海報是鋼鐵俠無限手套，上面寫著&ldquo;我們愛你3000遍&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\nAvengers 4 重映版時長188分鐘，比原版多​​了7分鐘。重映版究竟多了哪些內容，漫威官方解釋說：&ldquo;觀眾將看到來自羅素兄弟的介紹視頻，以及一個電影中未完成的刪除片段，而且觀眾還能通過特別先導預告，為即將到來的《蜘蛛俠：英雄遠征（Spider-Man: Far From Home）》做好準備！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n#Avengers4 重映將於6月28日開始（北美），同時也是 Spider-Man: Far From Home 在國內首映的日子。<br />\n<br />\n----<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAqyaBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAqyaBM.jpg&h=b6e65774&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33960b1dd09056aeb91c7ff689874b234a1bd31d","tid":1259352,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:25:05.000Z","msg":"香港唔會上？"},{"pid":"2629381f410f21c0ab8afd8c311e2ab8d54fd286","tid":1259352,"uid":55533,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:26:19.000Z","msg":"又要重刷幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea82e8504aa034cc6120fa3c5a33643b3091379","tid":1259352,"uid":269707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33960b1dd09056aeb91c7ff689874b234a1bd31d","tid":1259352,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:25:05.000Z","msg":"香港唔會上？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14: